Date: Mon, 18 May 2026 03:54:54 +0500
Subject: Support UnifiedPush as alternative push provider

---
 TMessagesProj/build.gradle                             |  1 +
 .../java/org/telegram/messenger/ApplicationLoader.java |  1 +
